festival.introText:
This Las Vegas festival will host an insane collection of pop-punk, emo, and hardcore acts at the Las Vegas Festival Grounds in October. The festival’s inaugural lineup in 2022 featured My Chemical Romance, Paramore, and Avril Lavigne, and was eventually expanded to three days due to overwhelming demand. 2023 is set to be an altogether more pop-punk affair with titans of the genre Green Day and Blink 182 headlining.

For every scene kid glued to Kerrang! during the mid 2000s, this is the festival for you. So grab your eyeliner, put on your Converse, and trek to the Nevada desert to relive the good times.
festival.festivalName: When We Were Young Music Festival
festival.location: Las Vegas USA in Las Vegas

faqs.question: When is When We Were Young 2023?
faqs.answer: When We Were Young takes place on Saturday 21st October 2023.

faqs.question: How to get to When We Were Young?
faqs.answer:
When We Were Young Festival will take place at:

Las Vegas Festival Grounds

311 W Sahara Avenue

Las Vegas, Nevada 89101

 

Festival grounds are ONLY accessible by walking, rideshare, and Las Vegas Monorail. NO access for passenger vehicles.

 

Flights

The Las Vegas Festival Grounds are located just a few miles from LAS (Harry Reid International Airport).

 

Walking

If you are staying on The Strip, it’s an easy walk to the festival:

  • 12 minute walk to Encore at Wynn Las Vegas
  • 25 minute walk to The Venetian & The Mirage
  • 30 minute walk to Caesars Palace

 

Las Vegas Monorail

Ride the Las Vegas Monorail to the SAHARA Las Vegas Station. Upon arrival, walk across the Monorail pedestrian bridge across Paradise Avenue and walk through SAHARA before crossing Las Vegas Blvd to enter festival grounds.

 

For more options, please see https://support.whenwewereyoungfestival.com/hc/en-us/articles/4418702608788-How-do-I-get-to-the-festival-

faqs.question: Are there any age restrictions at When We Were Young?
faqs.answer: No, When We Were Young is an all-ages event, but all festival attendees must be ticketed. VIP tickets are 21+.
